reviews.text: Rude staff. Card and cash payment options available. Very nice taste. Delicious options. Most sweets with mango are available. Many options in sweets and mango puddings. Many options in drinks. Seating available. Hui Lau Shan maintaining same standard across all it's outlets. Clean and well maintained place. Nice taste. Good and healthy food. Little crowded. Fast service. Thanks for the services.
Interesting choices -  however the white mix was not to any of our liking-  the mango mix was good -  none of the staff are able to communicate in English
Hated this place. Super lousy attitude by the guy in the picture. Shouted at me because I asked him to repeat because of noisy  traffic around. Don’t go.
Mango jelly was great!
Mango dessert is recommended

老香港的味道！

とっても美味しいです。
しかし有名なので店内はとても混んでますし内装とかも特にこだわって作った感じはなく狭いので隣の人との間隔がかなり近いです。
